div.div: Use case of OPTIONS, TRACE and HEAD Request Method

The first error is because MapStruct does not see Lombok annotated methods. Add the annotation processor to the build: org.mapstruct mapstruct-processor (6 more lines were trimmed) The second is that you add @Mapping to the list of objects, not the object itself. Create a method, which map a single Experience to ExperienceDTO, add the annotation there and remove it from the experienceToExperienceDTO method.
